{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.98\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">一篇诗。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">上帝掌管世界</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>你们要向耶和华唱新歌！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">因为他行过奇妙的事，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">他的右手和圣臂施行救恩。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>耶和华显明了他的救恩，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">在列国眼前显出公义；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>记念他对<span class=\"pn\">以色列</span>家的慈爱和信实。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">地的四极都看见我们上帝的救恩。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>全地都要向耶和华欢呼，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">要扬声，欢唱，歌颂！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>用琴歌颂耶和华，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">用琴和诗歌的声音歌颂他！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>用号筒和角声，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">在大君王耶和华面前欢呼！</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.7\" class=\"v7\">7</sup>愿海和其中所充满的澎湃，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\">愿世界和住在其间的发声。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v8\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.8\" class=\"v8\">8</sup>愿大水拍掌，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v8\">愿诸山在耶和华面前一同欢呼；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v9\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.9\" class=\"v9\">9</sup>因为他来要审判全地。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v9\">他要按公义审判世界，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v9\">按公正审判万民。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}